Tag Name:
  <input type="email">
  
Properties:
  None.
  
Description:
  The input value is automatically validated to ensure it is a properly formatted e-mail address.
  
Example:
<html>
  <body>

    <form>
      E-mail: <input type="email" name="emailaddress">
      <input type="submit">
    </form>

  </body>
</html>
